'''Advanced Micro Devices, Inc. (AMD)''' is a semiconductor company. AMD is most known for producing CPUs based on [[:wikipedia:x86|x86 intruction set]], motherboard chipsets and their own line GPUs.
Later AMD created [[AMD64|amd64]], which is the 64-bit equivalent instruction set of the x86.

